{"tid":2131321,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府押後選舉 卻產生更多法律問題 完美示範「搬石頭砸自己的腳」","createTime":"2020-07-29T19:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T19:06:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d38ecad45757f3d980e43717cccdd435ff7cd674","tid":2131321,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T19:01:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/BJ2ARD362LHFN7XRQBA27TY6Y4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FBJ2ARD362LHFN7XRQBA27TY6Y4%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=150c5bfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FBJ2ARD362LHFN7XRQBA27TY6Y4%2F&h=bb0aa37e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/BJ2ARD362LHFN7XRQBA27TY6Y4/</a><br />\n<br />\n2016年立法會DQ風波，觸發一連串補選及司法覆核，直到今年9月會期結束，仍有四個席位空缺，當中梁國雄和陳凱欣尚待上訴，區諾軒和范國威的官司已被終審法院駁回，惟選舉管理委員會以時間不足為由，不安排該兩席補選。政府倘若押後9月立法會大選，將現屆會立法會任期延長，區諾軒和范國威兩個席位大有可能要補選。有法律界人士表示，若到時安排補選，等於承認疫情下仍可以安全投票，估計為免尷尬局面，不排除政府索性禁止來年所有官方選舉。"},{"pid":"e4a711fbfbfc9681d9de5737e0a1694471367f19","tid":2131321,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T19:06:35.000Z","msg":"無問題啦, 佢把口話咩就係咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}